data.eml:eml: Two new species of Amphinemura (Plecoptera: Nemouridae) from Tibet

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Li, Weihai, Wang, Ying, Yang, Ding (2017): Two new species of Amphinemura (Plecoptera: Nemouridae) from Tibet. Zootaxa 4247 (4): 494-500, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4247.4.11
